nanos, and a complete thesaurus make this volume a valuable contribution to the study of late Byzantine literature.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 23. Jul 2020) 0aMilitary art and science. 4aBelagerung. 4aByzantine and Ottoman History. 4aGeschichte / 1422. 4aJohn Kananos. 4aKonstantinopel. 4aMedieval Greek. 4aOttomanen. 4aWarfare. 7aHISTORY / Medieval.2bisacsh1 aCuomo, Andrea Massimo, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus eBook-Package 2016z978311070100508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2016z9783110485103oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Classical Studies 2016z9783110485097oZDB-23-DGD0 cEPUBz97815015029030 cprintz978150151090840uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978150150288040uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9781501502880423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9781501502880.jpg  a978-3-11-070100-5  DG Plus eBook-Package 2016b2016  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_CL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_CL  aEBA_ECL_HICS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGDb2016  aZDB-23-DGGb2016